title: Mark Steyn in Sydney - Freedom of Speech Under Threat (29 Februa
description: Mark Steyn in Sydney, 29 February 2012. Function hosted by "Spectator Australia" and the "Institute of Public Affairs". Panelists also include Tom Switzer, Janet Albrechtsen and John Roskam. This is the full and untruncated audio file of the entire discussion, including the introductory comments and the question-&-answer session following Steyn's speech.
